 I have just arrived from Cybertron. I am looking for Magmatron, my "Nookie" 
key to the Destrons. I spent hours tracking across the world, eating 
cheezits, smelling my armpits, inspecting robots for "sensetive areas" and 
having a jolly bally time. There are new planets evolving. One is called 
"Powerpuff Squirel, my very own destron bang central. Well, The journey 
was....cheesy. I am here as I enter destron base, only to find cheezits, 
shredder, and that magmatron has left. So I speak flirtingly to shredder. 
"your heating up my metal parts, honeytron" I say.
